                    <br>Urban Legends.  A type of Desire.  “Was real” becomes a Rumor.
                    This kind of thinking was not strange to the world.  Since ancient times, a rumor was likely the accidental product of astronomical probability.
                    Looking from this way of thinking, the world was not chaotic, but orderly.
