                    And that Rumor is ...
                    <br />
                    <br />
                    In a past that was far too long ago.  The Old Deus competed with the ultimate prize of being the supreme, sole God on the line and started a war, along with their servants and created beings.
                    This war lasted for a long, long time.  So long it felt numbing.  There was no land that was not stained with blood, and cries of agony had never ceased to echo through the skies.
                    The civilized races hated each other, slaughtered each other, and continued to repeat their countless killings.  The Elves had small villages as their bases, and they cast magic to hunt their enemies.
